fields.title: 250 Schnapper Rock Road
fields.description: The grand entrance foyer leads you through to the multiple family living & dining areas, cleverly designed giving a peek of the adjacent rooms whilst also giving some privacy. Tailored to suit the current family of three; the third living area adjacent to the entrance is a delightful sitting/library room that could easily double as a home office or a perfect day nursery room if there was a new addition to your family. The warmth of the new *Coretec timber look flooring throughout the living, dining & kitchen areas offers the ultimate ease in terms of care for families, the brand new carpet in the three upstairs bedrooms, staircase & study nook is a dream to walk on.

fields.title: 14 Wainoni Heights, Greenhithe
fields.description:
Beautifully constructed and detailed, this newly completed home offers the epitome of the kiwi lifestyle. Modern with a casual elegance, it comes with the assurance of timeless quality and craftsmanship.

- Generous, light filled spaces

- Seamless indoor/outdoor living

- Sensational, designer kitchen with fully equipped scullery

- Thoughtful design to streamline family life

- Four large double bedrooms - two with ensuite and walk in wardrobe

- Plenty of room for cars, the boat and visitors

- Lush, established landscaping

- 10 year Master Build Guarantee

fields.title: 7 Headland Dr, Long Bay
fields.description:
One of the very few properties bordering the reserve, with an expansive elevated outlook, this luxury home is ideal for multi-generational / dual family living.

An entertainer's heaven featuring four living areas flowing to upper and lower level decks and wrap-around balconies sited superbly for sun and sensational ocean outlooks. A gourmet kitchen offering a stack of premium label Gaggenau appliances supports your hosting in fine style while a second kitchen and six bedrooms serviced by five beautiful bathrooms/ensuites lets extended family or guests enjoy independent living.
